import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import { Card, CardContent, Typography, Button, Grid, Table, TableHead, TableRow, TableCell, TableBody, Paper } from '@mui/material'; const PatientRecords = () => { const navigate = useNavigate(); const [appointments, setAppointments] = useState([]); const [recentPatients, setRecentPatients] = useState([]); useEffect(() => { const today = new Date().toISOString().slice(0, 10); // Sample Appointments setAppointments([ { time: '10:00 AM', name: 'Amit Shah', dept: 'Ortho', note: 'Braces check' }, { time: '11:30 AM', name: 'Sara Ali', dept: 'General', note: 'Tooth cleaning' } ]); // Sample Recent Patients setRecentPatients([ { name: 'Ravi Kumar', age: 32, phone: '9999999999', date: today, diagnosis: 'Cavity' }, { name: 'Anjali Menon', age: 25, phone: '8888888888', date: today, diagnosis: 'Root Canal' }, { name: 'Suresh Raina', age: 40, phone: '7777777777', date: today, diagnosis: 'Scaling' }, { name: 'Fatima Noor', age: 30, phone: '6666666666', date: today, diagnosis: 'Extraction' }, { name: 'Vikram Das', age: 29, phone: '5555555555', date: today, diagnosis: 'Crown' } ]); }, []); return (
